{"tid":1394360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來以前警疑涉非法集會","createTime":"2019-08-01T11:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T12:04:24.000Z","uid":66379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"228bc42c8630c2e05da5d576b24c402e72e02de2","tid":1394360,"uid":66379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:31:09.000Z","msg":"【七警案】撐警「會員大會」3.3萬人出席 出席者：要締造歷史<br />\n<br />\n台上亦有其他現役及退休警察發言，批評七警案裁決、表達對近年處理集會遊行積下的不滿等，更有人爆粗。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>就今次並無申請不反對通知書</strong></span>，而有<strong>3.3萬人集會</strong>，陳祖光在活動結束後強調，今次只是「協會代表大會」，屬內部事務，非隨便人能進入，而所有會員均有權出席，並非《公安條例》所規管的「集會」，又指人數是他始料不及。<br />\n<br />\n咁就唔洗apply不反對通加<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間:2017-02-22 20:00<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/73732/七警案-撐警-會員大會-3-3萬人出席-出席者-要締造歷史\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F73732%2F%E4%B8%83%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6-%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83-3-3%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD-%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E8%80%85-%E8%A6%81%E7%B7%A0%E9%80%A0%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEdDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=dd526ec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/73732/七警案-撐警-會員大會-3-3萬人出席-出席者-要締造歷史</a><br />\n<br />\n(香港01)"},{"pid":"550ea8fd9a6e3d397bf819442aa033617cac2086","tid":1394360,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:33:14.000Z","msg":"工聯會掌握香港各行業主要工會，手足快d去佢地fb支持下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394346</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3e8f62eea087d3f41eb383f49a0e020bd3f19b34","tid":1394360,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"}]}